name: Born Mucky: Life on the Farm
original_name: Born Mucky: Life on the Farm
overview: The reality of life for three modern-day British farmers and their families as they work to protect their land, livestock and legacy across the seasons, shining a light on those who work tirelessly to make a living off the land.
